Title: Authorizes the county of Cattaraugus to discontinue as parklands and lease certain reforested lands in the town of Perrysburg
Summary: Authorizes the county of Cattaraugus to discontinue as parklands and lease certain reforested lands in the town of Perrysburg.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the county of Cattaraugus to discontinue as parklands and lease certain reforested lands in the town of Perrysburg
